{"tid":665601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 元朗上海仔打警車　阿Sir「敗走」　 網民：12點後邊個話事?","createTime":"2018-05-15T05:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T07:39:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14295e1e3ecbf8883d6746797f33f48502857384","tid":665601,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391399&d=oxW6gKhhKw4scgCLfX8DVARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=424bf70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391399&h=97867199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391399</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月15日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n元朗上海仔打警車　阿Sir「敗走」　<br />\n網民：12點後邊個話事?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180515/large/a1202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180515%2Flarge%2Fa1202a.gif&h=f50e709d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n元朗12點後邊個話事?噚日網上熱傳一段影片，拍到前日母親節凌晨喺西裕街，一個着夏威夷恤嘅惡爺疑飲醉酒拍打衝鋒警車，仲「手指指」疑似指罵警員，奇怪嘅係警車上冇人有反應，慢慢駛走架警車就算數。而惡爺其後又俾一名更惡嘅陀地驅趕，成段片好似顯示邊個先係嗰度話事人咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180515/large/a1202b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180515%2Flarge%2Fa1202b.gif&h=7b81777e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■之後黑衣陀地出現，將惡爺喝退。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》查探後發現，拍打警車嘅惡爺係綽號「元朗上海仔」，有江湖中人話佢係過氣蠱惑仔，成日飲醉酒鬧事。事件惹起網民議論紛紛，質疑阿Sir對惡人軟弱得滯。貼片者更留言慨嘆：「到底片中邊個最大？12點之後元朗係邊個話事？」<br />\n<br />\n呢單「警察被蝦」喺周日凌晨3點發生，着夏威夷恤嘅「元朗上海仔」同兩個friend喺西裕街馬路打橫行，咁啱一部新界北衝鋒車路過，車上有三名警員，包括女警長、男警及司機。<br />\n<br />\n當時元朗上海仔突然走埋警車叫囂，先係拍打車身、車頭，跟住隔住擋風玻璃「手指指」疑似指罵車內嘅警員。同行者已幫忙拉開佢免衝突，警車上Madam懷疑見到對方飲醉咗，未有追究，衝鋒車就咁開走咗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n惡人遭更惡人喝退<br />\n<br />\n元朗上海仔繼續喺馬路上橫行，令人側目，但惡人自有惡人磨，無幾耐出現咗一個黑衣男，破口指罵佢：「你乜事啊你？嘈乜嘢啊？」黑衣男身邊仲出現咗六、七個大漢，追住元朗上海仔嚟鬧，一時間粗口滿天飛。元朗上海仔見唔對路，同朋友急急散水，短片至此結束。段片曝光後，大批網民留言質疑警方反應不夠強硬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180515/large/a1202c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180515%2Flarge%2Fa1202c.gif&h=b72b77e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識睇睇留言<br />\n<br />\nSteven：不可思議警察驚到即刻踩油走人！<br />\n<br />\nWah Wah Wan：新界自主，新界自決，新界獨立！<br />\n<br />\nJohn Chan：條片好清楚，警察要由黑幫解圍逃出險境！<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：《蘋果》網站  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 被指懦弱欠專業　傳車上3警遭照肺"},{"pid":"dda474cbc56e802103e43bee8614c3bef2247545","tid":665601,"uid":57489,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"有幾多個警察真係為左伸張正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家警察都係為左個兩皮先去做<br />\n<br />\n怕被人斬 鬼會搵命搏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022f2f0ad9b18d6e49aa2553cea74dbe449c3d26","tid":665601,"uid":45477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"12a0957f60be0beb7ef32c61f24ceebc5ada06fe","tid":665601,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"同一陣線 一人少句 好正常"},{"pid":"e8d833e74de307f007c47f8e65c0cb4ac19a76d6","tid":665601,"uid":164913,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a091a8a3aa924f936d511476b24b7de6cfc7020a","tid":665601,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,